German Chancellor Angela Merkel’s Father Dies at 85, DPA Reports

-- B y   C h r i s   R e i t e r
-- 
2011-09-03T09:32:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-03/german-chancellor-angela-merkel-s-father-dies-at-85-dpa-reports.html
German Chancellor  Angela Merkel ’s
father, Horst Kasner, died yesterday,  Deutsche Presse-Agentur 
reported, citing an unidentified government spokesman.  Merkel canceled an appearance at a rally today before
elections in the eastern state of Mecklenburg-Western Pomerania
for “family reasons,” the ruling CDU party said in a
statement. Kasner was 85, DPA reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chris Reiter in Berlin at 
 creiter2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
